data.description: Welcome home to this stunning 5 bedroom, 3 and a half bath home. This beautiful  2-story home has a comfortable & spacious lay out, making you feel right at home. When you first enter the home, it boasts a huge den on the 1st floor, then leading into the open concept floor plan with the perfect sized kitchen with walk in pantry. The kitchen flows into the cozy living room & dining area looking out to your fenced in back yard. The large master bedroom and bath is also located downstairs, along with your conveniently placed half bath. With several closets throughout the home, there is more than plenty of storage. The upstairs has the 4 other bedrooms, all with walk in closets, along with a huge additional living space with endless possibilities. It currently has a T.V room with a fully working 2nd kitchen, which can easily stay or go at the buyers convenience.   UPGRADES INCLUDE: NEW ROOF & NEW FLOORING THROUGHOUT. This charming 2 car garage property is situated on a peaceful cul-de-sac in a beautiful neighborhood. Additionally, the low HOA fees make this home even more desirable, providing added value and peace of mind.   Located in the well sought out Four Corners, you'll enjoy easy access to a variety of restaurants, shops, and amenities. Whether you're looking for a cozy dinner spot or a vibrant shopping experience, this location has it all.    The neighborhood is surrounded by top-rated schools, ensuring a quality education for your little ones.     Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this house your dream home. Contact us today to schedule a viewing and experience the beauty and convenience this property has to offer.  ***More pictures coming soon!***
